{"tid":2171513,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"全民抵制檢測係一種表態 我哋要落共產黨面","createTime":"2020-08-24T03:53:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-01T10:39:52.000Z","uid":331739,"like":21,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"48134705b07d3730557981c31dafb7a36f0562bf","tid":2171513,"uid":331739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T03:53:26.000Z","msg":"而家個重點唔係檢測有冇用 而係我唔信你呢個政府<br />\n過去一年香港人搞到你雞毛鴨血 絕對唔會咁好心無啦啦同你驗<br />\n而家港共已經開曬聲 叫人去驗 驗完又收集咗DNA 又可以多謝中央<br />\n到時又可以話唔係中央幫香港 香港就玩完了<br />\n所以我哋唔驗 就係一種表態 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n驗都無人去驗 佢點多謝中央？?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中央咁偉大出手幫香港同胞 比香港人良心當狗肺 仲唔好嬲好嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n外國煤媒: 北京協助港抗疫 港人集體抵制<br />\n共產黨：<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0f2d4b3da045d7e285c38af60e559a4bd6726aa","tid":2171513,"uid":10503,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T03:55:53.000Z","msg":"總之而家佢推咩我就反咩<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NZafHGA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNZafHGA.jpg&h=3576d00b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9796281f64372697d05936dfa0f2a4b97d74e005","tid":2171513,"uid":331739,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e0f2d4b3da045d7e285c38af60e559a4bd6726aa","tid":2171513,"uid":10503,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T03:55:53.000Z","msg":"總之而家佢推咩我就反咩<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NZafHGA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNZafHGA.jpg&h=3576d00b&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T03:56:55.000Z","msg":"逼到佢強制要全部人驗囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/